----- stdout -----
Show inter-module dependency graph for the entire crate

Usage: crawk deps [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -t, --include-tests           Include modules defined in `#[cfg(test)]` blocks (excluded by default)
  -d, --depth <DEPTH>           Truncate module paths to at most N segments.
  -f, --format <FORMAT>         Output format [default: plain] [possible values: plain, grouped, dot]
      --cycles [<CYCLES>]       Detect and display dependency cycles (strongly connected components) [possible values: detect, highlight]
  -a, --show-apis               Show API names (symbols) that create each dependency edge
      --orphans                 List modules with no incoming dependencies (orphans)
      --path <SOURCE> <TARGET>  Show all shortest dependency paths from SOURCE to TARGET
  -h, --help                    Print help (see more with '--help')

----- stderr -----
